- `game/.intel/execution.log` — this log
- `game/index.html` — entry point with HUD, tab bar, content panels
- `game/styles/main.css` — full dark-theme CSS (BEM, CSS custom properties)
- `game/src/main.js` — boot sequence, save/load, control binding
