- `game/src/utils/logger.js` — debug logger (no-op in production)
- `game/src/utils/fmt.js` — fmtNum(), fmtRate(), fmtTime()

**Architecture decisions:**
- Vanilla ES modules, no build step — opens directly in browser
- 250ms tick loop (4 ticks/s) with pluggable system registration
- Single state object, all mutations via actions.js
- Pub/sub events decouple systems from UI
- 15% per-building cost scaling for build inflation
- Save/load via localStorage with auto-save every 60s

