**Tasks completed:** T013, T014

**Summary:**
Implemented the full random event system and quest/objective system, completing Phase 4's two gameplay-enriching features.

**Files created:**
- `game/src/systems/randomEvents.js` — 10 weighted random events (raids/windfalls/disasters), 120–240s interval timer, temporary rate modifier system
- `game/src/systems/quests.js` — 11 milestone quests with check predicates and resource rewards; event-driven completion detection; `setQuestPanelRenderer()` hook avoids circular imports
