- Speed multiplier lives only in `tick.js` — not persisted to save, so game always starts at 1× on load (intentional; saves should not carry a "paused at 4× speed" state).
- Settings panel re-renders on every speed button click rather than mutating DOM — keeps it stateless and simple given it's rarely visited.

