**Files modified:**
- `game/src/ui/settingsPanel.js` — Imported `exportSave`/`importSave` from `saveModal.js`. Added a "💾 Save Portability" section to the settings panel HTML with Export Save and Import Save buttons; bound them in `_render()` via `panel.querySelector`.
